PRIMARILY IN OUR PHONE HARDWARE BUSINESS. AS A RESULT OF THE NDS ACQUISITION, WE HAVE CERTAIN EMPLOYEES THAT ARE SUBJECT TO COLLECTIVE BARGAINING AGREEMENTS.

AVAILABLE INFORMATION

OUR INTERNET ADDRESS IS WWW.MICROSOFT.COM. AT OUR INVESTOR RELATIONS

