OF OFFICE AND DATA CENTER SPACE DOMESTICALLY (OUTSIDE OF THE PUGET SOUND CORPORATE CAMPUS) AND LEASE MANY SITES DOMESTICALLY TOTALING APPROXIMATELY FIVE MILLION SQUARE FEET OF OFFICE AND DATA CENTER SPACE.

