SHARE REPURCHASES

ON SEPTEMBER 16, 2013, OUR BOARD OF DIRECTORS APPROVED A SHARE REPURCHASE PROGRAM AUTHORIZING UP TO $40.0 BILLION IN SHARE REPURCHASES. THE SHARE REPURCHASE PROGRAM BECAME EFFECTIVE ON OCTOBER 1, 2013,

