NOTE 21  EMPLOYEE STOCK AND SAVINGS PLANS

WE GRANT STOCK-BASED COMPENSATION TO DIRECTORS AND EMPLOYEES. AT JUNE 30, 2015, AN AGGREGATE OF 294 MILLION SHARES

WERE AUTHORIZED FOR FUTURE GRANT UNDER OUR STOCK PLANS. AWARDS THAT EXPIRE OR ARE CANCELED WITHOUT DELIVERY OF SHARES GENERALLY BECOME AVAILABLE FOR ISSUANCE UNDER THE PLANS. WE ISSUE NEW SHARES OF MICROSOFT COMMON STOCK TO SATISFY EXERCISES AND

VESTING OF AWARDS GRANTED UNDER ALL OF OUR STOCK PLANS.

