STOCK PLANS

STOCK

AWARDS

STOCK AWARDS (SAS) ARE GRANTS THAT ENTITLE THE HOLDER TO SHARES OF MICROSOFT COMMON STOCK AS THE AWARD VESTS.

SAS GENERALLY VEST OVER A FOUR OR FIVE-YEAR PERIOD.

